com.scalar.dl.ledger.crypto

Class SecretEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.scalar.dl.ledger.crypto.SecretEntry

  • @Immutable
public class SecretEntry
extends java.lang.Object
    Container for a registered HMAC secret key and metadata about the secret key. In addition to the secret key, a SecretEntry has:
    • the entity ID that has the secret key
    • the version of the secret key
    • the time at which the secret key was registered
